# Deny by default: only files required by the application and WhisperX builds
# may enter the Docker build context. Local env files, private media, Git data,
# caches, tests, docs, and agent state therefore never reach the builder.
**
!.dockerignore
!Dockerfile
!pyproject.toml
!uv.lock
!src/
!src/**
!scripts/
!scripts/**
!services/
!services/**
